# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VideoForge AI — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env.local for local dev, add to Vercel for production
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Supabase (Database + Auth) ───────────────────────────
# Required for: user accounts, persistent storage, multi-user
# Get from: Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...your-anon-key

# ── Anthropic (Script Generation) ────────────────────────
# Required for: AI-generated video scripts, thumbnails
# Get from: console.anthropic.com → API Keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── ElevenLabs (Voice Generation) ────────────────────────
# Required for: AI narration/voiceover
# Get from: elevenlabs.io → Profile → API Key
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=sk_...

# ── Vercel Cron (Job Processing) ─────────────────────────
# Required for: background job processing security
# Generate: any random secret string
CRON_SECRET=your-random-secret-here

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NOTES:
# - App works in DEMO MODE without any env vars (localStorage only)
# - Add Supabase vars first for persistent storage
# - Add Anthropic key for real script generation
# - Add ElevenLabs for real voiceover
# - YouTube/TikTok/Instagram/Facebook OAuth tokens are stored
#   per-channel in the database after user connects their accounts
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
